{"tid":2041153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家搞清楚，「黃藍是政見」「黑白是良知」，勿以顏色去區分。","createTime":"2020-05-29T05:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T06:05:13.000Z","uid":19218,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b526b523cebb99516070c13394708e97e0dc7fc5","tid":2041153,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:03:59.000Z","msg":"近呢幾個月成日批鬥黃絲/黃圈，我想指出黃藍只係政見，<br />\n<br />\n每個人都有唔同人格品行，有啲人就算佢支持社運都唔代<br />\n<br />\n表佢品格係一定岩<br />\n<br />\n希望大家理性睇清楚，政見可以一樣，但大家處事手法可<br />\n<br />\n以相差好遠。<br />\n<br />\n唔好批鬥黃藍，盡量以事論事，唔好乜都拉黃藍黎講。"},{"pid":"45999bfd2b4510d25dc1ca5551541afd04f2f915","tid":2041153,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:18:07.000Z","msg":"我係咪講錯野"},{"pid":"f715d858037ef54c0f8cd4bc5ad5c9e8e65d7bbd","tid":2041153,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:45:57.000Z","msg":"人如其名"},{"pid":"1f2c44bb49869bc8a7ad8accc46963a563924d7b","tid":2041153,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45999bfd2b4510d25dc1ca5551541afd04f2f915","tid":2041153,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:18:07.000Z","msg":"我係咪講錯野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"依家上來講無用<br />\n連登平日office hour最多5毛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n龍門收美金單野，5毛露晒底<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2039509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2039509</a>"}]}